28int
29GenericGFPoly::evaluateAt(int a) const
30{
31 if (a == 0) {
32 // Just return the x^0 coefficient
33 return coefficient(0);
34 }
35 if (a == 1) {
36 // Just the sum of the coefficients
37 int result = 0;
38 for (int coef : _coefficients) {
39 result = _field->addOrSubtract(result, coef);
40 }
41 return result;
42 }
43 int result = _coefficients[0];
44 for (size_t i = 1; i < _coefficients.size(); ++i) {
45 result = _field->addOrSubtract(_field->multiply(a, result), _coefficients[i]);
46 }
47 return result;
48}
49
50GenericGFPoly& GenericGFPoly::addOrSubtract(GenericGFPoly& other)
51{
52 assert(_field == other._field); // "GenericGFPolys do not have same GenericGF field"
53
54 if (isZero()) {
55 swap(*this, other);
56 return *this;
57 }
58
59 if (other.isZero()) {
60 return *this;
61 }
62
63 auto& smallerCoefs = other._coefficients;
64 auto& largerCoefs = _coefficients;
65 if (smallerCoefs.size() > largerCoefs.size())
66 std::swap(smallerCoefs, largerCoefs);
67
68 size_t lengthDiff = largerCoefs.size() - smallerCoefs.size();
69
70 // high-order terms only found in higher-degree polynomial's coefficients stay untouched
71 for (size_t i = lengthDiff; i < largerCoefs.size(); ++i)
72 largerCoefs[i] = _field->addOrSubtract(smallerCoefs[i - lengthDiff], largerCoefs[i]);
73
74 normalize();
75 return *this;
76}
77
78GenericGFPoly&
79GenericGFPoly::multiply(const GenericGFPoly& other)
80{
81 assert(_field == other._field); // "GenericGFPolys do not have same GenericGF field"
82
83 if (isZero() || other.isZero())
84 return _field->setZero(*this);
85
86 auto& a = _coefficients;
87 auto& b = other._coefficients;
88
89 // To disable the use of the malloc cache, simply uncomment:
90 // Coefficients _cache;
91 _cache.resize(a.size() + b.size() - 1);
92 std::fill(_cache.begin(), _cache.end(), 0);
93 for (size_t i = 0; i < a.size(); ++i) {
94 for (size_t j = 0; j < b.size(); ++j) {
95 _cache[i + j] = _field->addOrSubtract(_cache[i + j], _field->multiply(a[i], b[j]));
96 }
97 }
98
99 _coefficients.swap(_cache);
100
101 normalize();
102 return *this;
103}
104
105GenericGFPoly&
106GenericGFPoly::multiply(int scalar)
107{
108 if (scalar == 0) {
109 return _field->setZero(*this);
110 }
111 if (scalar == 1) {
112 return *this;
113 }
114
115 for (int& c : _coefficients) {
116 c = _field->multiply(c, scalar);
117 }
118
119 normalize();
120 return *this;
121}
122
123GenericGFPoly&
124GenericGFPoly::multiplyByMonomial(int degree, int coefficient)
125{
126 assert(degree >= 0);
127
128 if (coefficient == 0) {
129 return _field->setZero(*this);
130 }
131 size_t size = _coefficients.size();
132 for (size_t i = 0; i < size; ++i) {
133 _coefficients[i] = _field->multiply(_coefficients[i], coefficient);
134 }
135 _coefficients.resize(size + degree, 0);
136
137 normalize();
138 return *this;
139}
140
141GenericGFPoly&
142GenericGFPoly::divide(const GenericGFPoly& other, GenericGFPoly& quotient)
143{
144 assert(_field == other._field); // "GenericGFPolys do not have same GenericGF field"
145
146 if (other.isZero()) {
147 throw std::invalid_argument("Divide by 0");
148 }
149
150 _field->setZero(quotient);
151 auto& remainder = *this;
152
153 int denominatorLeadingTerm = other.coefficient(other.degree());
154 int inverseDenominatorLeadingTerm = _field->inverse(denominatorLeadingTerm);
155
156 ZX_THREAD_LOCAL GenericGFPoly temp;
157
158 while (remainder.degree() >= other.degree() && !remainder.isZero()) {
159 int degreeDifference = remainder.degree() - other.degree();
160 int scale = _field->multiply(remainder.coefficient(remainder.degree()), inverseDenominatorLeadingTerm);
161 _field->setMonomial(temp, degreeDifference, scale);
162 quotient.addOrSubtract(temp);
163 temp = other;
164 temp.multiplyByMonomial(degreeDifference, scale);
165 remainder.addOrSubtract(temp);
166 }
167
168 return *this;
169}
170
171void GenericGFPoly::normalize()
172{
173 auto& coefs = _coefficients;
174 auto firstNonZero = std::find_if(coefs.cbegin(), coefs.cend(), [](int c){ return c != 0; });
175 // Leading term must be non-zero for anything except the constant polynomial "0"
176 if (firstNonZero != coefs.cbegin())
177 {
178 if (firstNonZero == coefs.end()) {
179 coefs.resize(1, 0);
180 }
181 else {
182 std::copy(firstNonZero, coefs.cend(), coefs.begin());
183 coefs.resize(coefs.cend() - firstNonZero);
184 }
185 }
186}
